window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Top 40 in the entire Kindle Store!</b></p> <p><b>It's the dawn of a new age....</b></p> <p>Secrets—you know my family is founded on them. </p> <p><i>You just don’t know how much they’re suffocating us. </i></p> <p>Lies—my marriage hinges on one. </p> <p><i>You know that I chose to protect the wrong woman. </i></p> <p>I kept the past buried like a coward. Now, I feel the constraints of my choices like they’re a chokehold. </p> <p>I know that it’s time to tell my wife the truth. </p> <p>It’s time to deal with the consequences of my actions. </p> <p>Aoife deserves to be my judge, jury, and executioner. </p> <p>If she burns down the house with me in it, well, that’s on me and my filthy secrets….</p> <p><i>This is Aoife O’Grady’s story....</i></p>"; 
